bs. That would make a new year’s resolution of prosperity in 2016 a dream come true for the winners.</p>\n<p>But not likely!</p>\n<p>The chart below shows your odds of winning the top prize. In reality, buying a lottery ticket is nothing more than a regressive, voluntary tax. That said, someone will win the top prize and that’s what keeps America playing the lottery. Our success as a country was built on, and always will be, a nation of dreamers&#8212;no matter what the odds of success are!</p>\n<p>Good luck!</p>\n<p><span class=\"wp-image-1246 aligncenter inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:841px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:59.523809523809526%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/f286ad0324587955d7a074a223bb4584/9c4c6/c81c7be226ccea64fbaab4c723ae4b67.png 210w,\n/static/f286ad0324587955d7a074a223bb4584/fe69c/c81c7be226ccea64fbaab4c723ae4b67.png 421w,\n/static/f286ad0324587955d7a074a223bb4584/20595/c81c7be226ccea64fbaab4c723ae4b67.png 841w,\n/static/f286ad0324587955d7a074a223bb4584/5ece7/c81c7be226ccea64fbaab4c723ae4b67.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 841px) 100vw, 841px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 841px) 100vw, 841px\" srcSet=\"/static/f286ad0324587955d7a074a223bb4584/9c4c6/c81c7be226ccea64fbaab4c723ae4b67.png 210w,\n/static/f286ad0324587955d7a074a223bb4584/fe69c/c81c7be226ccea64fbaab4c723ae4b67.png 421w,\n/static/f286ad0324587955d7a074a223bb4584/20595/c81c7be226ccea64fbaab4c723ae4b67.png 841w,\n/static/f286ad0324587955d7a074a223bb4584/5ece7/c81c7be226ccea64fbaab4c723ae4b67.png 1200w\" src=\"/static/f286ad0324587955d7a074a223bb4584/20595/c81c7be226ccea64fbaab4c723ae4b67.png\" alt=\"Expected Powerball Payout Chart\" loading=\"eage